init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was about to ask him if he had been in a relationship before, but he disappeared right in front of her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was convinced that she had seen him there, and wasn’t just going crazy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She decided to call her friends for help.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What does he want from her?
